{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Can you build smart decks and defend your territory? I believe in you...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Queen's Cards is a strategy defense game featuring over 50 different card options. With towers, special upgrades, military units, spells, economy cards, and unique deck enhancements, it offers players a variety of playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3519780/extras/cardgif.gif?t=1740748317\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To defend your territory, you must strategically position your towers and use your cards at the right time. While doing this, you need to manage your economy carefully and calculate card costs wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You should choose tower-specific <strong>Skill Tree</strong> upgrades and the special buildings you construct in your territory carefully. Be prepared for different types of enemies that grow stronger with each wave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pay attention to your military units and fight alongside them against incoming enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3519780/extras/\u0130simsiz_video.gif?t=1740748317\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Good luck protecting your queen in the fantastic and surprise-filled world of <strong>Queen\u2019s Cards</strong>, my friend!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3519780?t=1740748317","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3519780?t=1740748317","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3519780/be5aaee7ccf7bf8452b40b29